commit.message:
Delete `no change needed' messages.

From-SVN: r3089

files.patch:
@@ -189,7 +189,6 @@ while [ $# != 0 ]; do
 	' $2/$file > $2/$file.sed
 	mv $2/$file.sed $2/$file
 	if cmp $file $2/$file >/dev/null 2>&1; then
-	   echo Deleting $2/$file\; no fixes were needed.
 	   rm $2/$file
 	fi
       fi

   else
